                "summary": "Our new study, published in Nature Astronomy, has now tested Einstein\u2019s theory on the largest of scales. We believe our approach may one day help resolve some of the biggest mysteries in cosmology, and the results hint that the theory of general relativity may need to be tweaked on this scale.",
