                    "The couple, from Corstorphine in Edinburgh, had booked the \u00a34498 trip in June with Marella Cruises, which is run by travel giant TUI, to celebrate their July 2020 wedding. They boarded the vessel on January 24 at Montego Bay port in Jamaica for a two-week voyage taking in the Cayman Islands, Cuba, Mexico and Jamaica before heading to Colombia, Panama and Costa Rica.",
