                "title": "Tamron continues to play with the boundaries of standard zoom lenses",
                "summary": "Newly uncovered patents show Tamron is aiming to reinvent the standard zoom lens focal length (again)",
                "publish_date": "Sat, 04 Feb 2023 06:36:32 GMT",
